Rescue workers: Pre-scenario briefing



All the group campsites around ours were taken by people (largely firemen and policemen) taking part in rescue training exercises. Here one of the instructors talks to some of them before a rescue.
Taken Saturday, October 12, 2002, 12:20:45pm.  Original image size: 2703x1802, 7.5Mb
